    <key>readme</key>
    <string>Splynek workflow.

Keywords:
  dl &lt;url&gt;        — download the URL via Splynek
  dlq &lt;url&gt;       — append to the Splynek queue
  dlstatus        — list active downloads

Requires Splynek.app to be running. The workflow calls splynek.sh
which reads ~/Library/Application Support/Splynek/fleet.json for the
port + token, then hits the local HTTP API.</string>
